some more time?

14:29.120 --> 14:32.380
Yes, but Dr. Shepherd doesn't
think that's a good idea.

14:32.380 --> 14:34.120
She didn't say that.

14:34.120 --> 14:36.920
Didn't say, "I want to"
or "I need to."

14:36.920 --> 14:38.500
She said, "I could."

14:41.080 --> 14:43.000
That's what we tell
our patients

14:43.000 --> 14:45.210
