17:18.420 --> 17:20.750
Mnh-mnh, mnh-mnh.

17:20.750 --> 17:22.620
Mnh-mnh, what?

17:22.620 --> 17:24.040
I get
why he's mad at you.

17:24.040 --> 17:25.460
