20:22.120 --> 20:23.790
but you're not giving me
anything to go on.

20:23.790 --> 20:25.500
[ Sighing ] Oh, man.

20:25.500 --> 20:28.290
We have been going around and
around with this for months.

20:28.290 --> 20:29.830
I feel
like I don't know you.

20:31.420 --> 20:34.920
And everybody that I know
that knows you...

20:34.920 --> 20:36.710
they don't like you.
[ Chuckles ]

20:36.710 --> 20:38.080
And you just
keep making jokes

20:38.080 --> 20:40.460
like somehow
that doesn't matter to me.

20:40.460 --> 20:42.170
That's not true.

20:42.170 --> 20:43.540
This isn't up to me
to make a choice.

20:43.540 --> 20:46.000
